tspan.tspan: In this project we develop a distributed Open Point Cloud Map (OPCM)
infrastructure to support data sharing and to enables interactive real-time
visualization using perspective views. We aim to develop a 3D point cloud
viewer without data density shocks, continuous zoom-in/out and progressive data
streaming between server and client.The reusable Open Source tooling we develop
is implemented for the Dutch Elevation Model (AHN) and can be accessed via:
